content:
i'm designing a video game about vacationing. we have created a list of vacation activities, including their title and duration. there are other properties mentioned, but you can ignore those.

please look through the CSV, and generate a new CSV by filling in the "Specific Title" row with a more specific themed example — such as starbucks, ice skating, hiking, meditating — depending on the duration and existing title.

for example, the first row of the CSV is:

Eat Indoors,1,

Here is a valid output for this row:

Eat Indoors,1,Starbucks

Below is the full CSV. Please reply with your updated CSV that fills out the "Specific Title" I requested above:
